data.description:
Back on Market!! Looking to own your first home in
Florida? This quaint little home is nestled in the Meadowbrook neighborhood of Orange Park, close to shopping and entertainment and all that
Blanding Boulevard has to offer. This home has a fully fenced in back yard. Very close distance to W.E Cherry Elementary School. This home has
been recently updated with NEW HVAC in 2022, ROOF in 2019. New luxury vinyl plank throughout. Kitchen has been recently updated and entire
home was painted. A true must see! Before it is gone! Contact us today for your private showing!
